Commodities Extend Decline After U.S. Jobs Report Signals Slower Growth

-- B y   S h a r o n   L i n d o r e s
-- 
2011-09-02T12:36:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-02/commodities-extend-decline-after-u-s-jobs-report-signals-slower-growth.html
The S&P GSCI Index of 24 commodities
sank 1.4 percent by 1:35 p.m. in  London  on the U.S. jobs report.
Silver, gold and wheat were the top performers.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
